<?xml version='1.0' encoding='ISO-8859-1' ?>
<grammar>
<section>
<title>&lt;i&gt; want/want to&lt;/i&gt;  </title>
<sectiontitle>We use &lt;i&gt;want +&lt;/i&gt; noun.</sectiontitle>
<titlesound>sta_gram12_1_1.mp3</titlesound>
<text1>I &lt;b&gt;want&lt;/b&gt; a &lt;b&gt;magazine.&lt;/b&gt;</text1>
<text1a>She doesn't &lt;b&gt;want&lt;/b&gt; any &lt;b&gt;boots.&lt;/b&gt;</text1a>
<sound1>sta_gram12_1_2.mp3</sound1>
<text2></text2>
<text2a>Do you &lt;b&gt;want&lt;/b&gt; some &lt;b&gt;jeans?&lt;/b&gt;</text2a>
<sound2>sta_gram12_1_3.mp3</sound2>
<sectiontitle2>We use &lt;i&gt;want to&lt;/i&gt; + verb.</sectiontitle2>
<titlesound2>sta_gram12_1_4.mp3</titlesound2>
<text3>We &lt;b&gt;want to watch&lt;/b&gt; a football match.</text3>
<text3a>She doesn't &lt;b&gt;want to buy&lt;/b&gt; any flowers.</text3a>
<sound3>sta_gram12_1_5.mp3</sound3>
<text4></text4>
<text4a>Do you &lt;b&gt;want to drive&lt;/b&gt; to the airport?</text4a>
<sound4>sta_gram12_1_6.mp3</sound4>
</section>
</grammar>